metadata.name: Flower Girl.AI #1
metadata.description:
A collection of 333 Flower Girls ready to bloom into the Metaverse.

A flower blooms,
So delicate and fair,
A symbol of new life,
Fresh and vibrant, everywhere.

A girl blooms too,
As she grows and learns,
Her potential unfurling,
Like the petals of a fern.

Together they bloom,
In perfect harmony,
A beauty to behold,
A sight for all to see.

The flower and the girl,
Both graceful and serene,
Their spirits soaring,
As they blossom and gleam.

So let us all bloom,
Like the flower and the girl,
And let our light shine,
In a world that can often swirl.
